ATOMS WERE BUILT USING STEREOCHEMICAL CONSTRAINTS AND
KEPT IN THE COORDINATE FILE.

WATER MOLECULES 272 AND 273 ARE ON A TWO-FOLD AXIS AND HAVE
BEEN MODELED WITH 50% OCCUPANCY.
;
